{"tid":2203830,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"一聞「970士巴拿」 警方即閃人 區議員：乜警隊好缺人？","createTime":"2020-09-15T15:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T02:32:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f9bd0c682eccdae0c9f3d1a2fb34ef770b6e69d6","tid":2203830,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T15:02:18.000Z","msg":"本月6日嘅九龍遊行，警方指一名新巴970號線車長喺彌敦道「無故響號」及「快速行駛」，指控車長藏有士巴拿，將佢拘捕，並控以一項不小心駕駛罪。民主黨3位區議員曾自鳴、李偉峰、朱子洛今日（15日）喺區議會交通及運輸事務委員會就此事提出緊急討論，警方一聞「970士巴拿」色變，急急腳話有事，拉隊走人。藍絲都話啦，冇犯法怕咩嘢，究竟班警察怕乜呢？<br />\n<br />\n警務處代表甄翰揚話，佢只係依照上司嘅指示離開，仲好不屑咁話：「可能大家把尺唔同。」啱呀，警方把尺，從來都同香港人唔同。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/YKB5FWRFBFHFBM2GFAYZP4QM6Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2FYKB5FWRFBFHFBM2GFAYZP4QM6Y%2F&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIueBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=be7b49b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2FYKB5FWRFBFHFBM2GFAYZP4QM6Y%2F&h=804118cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/YKB5FWRFBFHFBM2GFAYZP4QM6Y/</a>"},{"pid":"548461c0d163cc34fe3e8575952a86d6a34f4c29","tid":2203830,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T15:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c8135aa91f739f26999cc1d5aa8ec856ee1532c","tid":2203830,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T15:03:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"862f5b73d195d204b7066e6026ab5164f72bf63b","tid":2203830